Package org.kj.blackjack.player

Class AbstractPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kj.blackjack.player.AbstractPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Player

    public abstract class AbstractPlayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Player
    Contains utility methods for a Blackjack player as well as abstract methods for the player's most complex action, which is to choose either HIT or STAND.
